Reasoning: The paper deals with under-determined linear systems of equations with sparse solutions, which is a core problem in compressed sensing. The paper also discusses the $\ell_1$-minimization technique and its threshold behavior. These topics are closely related to information theory (cs.IT), signal processing (cs.SP), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and data structures (cs.DS).
